 results are therefore consistent with a picture in which mergers\ncan (but don't always) trigger AGN activity, but where the majority of galaxies\nhosting high luminosity AGN are not recent mergers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 14 Dec 2022 17:07:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-28"}
