most requests\nare provided by the two largest portions of providers in the system, located in\nNorth America and Europe. With these insights, we conclude that the current\nIPFS architecture is sub-optimal and propose a research agenda for the future.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 14 Dec 2022 17:53:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-15"}
