 in the buffet\nrange suggest broadband fluctuations at Strouhal numbers between 0.2 and 0.6,\nwhich is consistent with recent literature. The spanwise shock propagation\nvelocities were determined independently via analysis of unsteady PSP and\npressure transducers to be in the range between $u_s / u_{\\infty} = 0.24$ and\n$0.32$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 14 Dec 2022 19:58:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-31"}
