ion as a primary mechanism behind the lossy nature of internal bores.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 15 Dec 2022 13:30:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 24 Apr 2023 11:17:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-23"}
