be not related to temperature gradients. The temperature\nconfiguration of equilibration simulation employing the dropout uncertainty\nneural network potential with a dropout rate of 0.1 is reported to be the most\naccurate compared with the rest. This work is expected to inspire further\ninvestigation of non-equilibrium dynamics in graphene with practical\napplications in various engineering fields.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 15 Dec 2022 15:34:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 15 May 2023 18:04:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-17"}
