 is implemented and will be applied in a continuous\nvideo processing system running on a camera network covering a 4-mile stretch\nof Interstate-24 near Nashville, Tennessee.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 15 Dec 2022 15:39:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-16"}
